{"title":"判断用户有没有登录过(利用cookie)","slug":"判断用户有没有登录过(利用cookie)","date":"2017-09-20T01:59:08.913Z","updated":"2017-09-16T05:25:07.148Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"判断用户有没有登录过\"><a href=\"#判断用户有没有登录过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"判断用户有没有登录过\"></a>判断用户有没有登录过</h2></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>获取用户名和头像</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> userInfoStr = $.cookie(<span class=\"string\">\"userInfo\"</span>);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>判断：</p>\n  <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!userInfoStr)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    location.href = <span class=\"string\">\"login.html\"</span></div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[{"name":"开发技巧","path":"api/categories/开发技巧.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"开发技巧","path":"api/tags/开发技巧.json"}]}